= SDL_GetRGBA =
Use this function to map a pixel value into the RGBA components for a given pixel format.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_GetRGBA(Uint32   	        pixel,
		 const SDL_PixelFormat* format,
		 Uint8*  	        r,
		 Uint8*  	        g,
		 Uint8*  	        b,
		 Uint8*  	        a)
```

